@Rapptz You might have to document this in Discord.py as it is not documented in ytdl yet as far as I know of. If they want to have their bot search and/or if they want to silent ytdl on their console they simply need this code.
```py
class YTDLLogger(object):
    def debug(self, msg):
        pass

    def warning(self, msg):
        pass

    def error(self, msg):
        pass

# youtube_dl options
ytdlo = {'quiet': True, 'no_warnings': True, 'ignoreerrors': True, 'logger': YTDLLogger(), 'default_search': "ytsearch"}
```

Also the console silence from it is of cource optional too.

